text: Amazon IoT is a service that lets you securely connect your devices to the cloud without the need to host your own gateways or proxies. It handles authentication, data encryption, device handling and integration with other AWS services. Built on top of MQTT, it adds functionality for device state handling called shadows, which greatly simplifies offline device handling.
title: Breakfast Seminar on IoT
